response.overview: With Captain Barnacles, Kwazii, Peso and the rest of the Octonauts crew every day is an exciting opportunity to embark on a new mission! In these episodes Kwazii explores a pirate shipwreck in search of a mythical sword, Barnacles struggles to free his paw from the mouth of a giant clam and the Octonauts must figure out how to rescue a gigantic saltwater crocodile from freezing waters. Episodes: Porcupine Puffer, Scared Sperm Whale, Long Arm Squid, Swashbuckling Swordfish, Manatees, Saltwater Crocodile, Humphead Parrotfish.
response.title: Octonauts Calling All Gups
